<PageTitle>Memory Game - How to Play</PageTitle>

<h1>How to Play</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to the Memory Game! The goal is to match all the pairs of cards as quickly as possible and with the fewest moves.
</p>
<ol>
    <li>Choose a difficulty level on the Home Page.</li>
    <li>Click "Play" to start the game.</li>
    <li>Select two cards to reveal them.</li>
    <li>If they match, they'll remain visible; otherwise, they'll flip back over.</li>
    <li>Match all pairs to complete the game.</li>
    <li>Save your score and challenge yourself to improve!</li>
</ol>
